### 注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 登录，复制 token 到下面变量
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 活动列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 预热全部活动库存到 Redis
POST http://localhost:8080/api/activities/preload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 秒杀，活动时间为 2026-06-18 20:00:00
POST http://localhost:8080/api/seckill/grab
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "activityId": 900001
}

### 报名抽奖，开奖时间为 2026-06-18 20:45:00
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lottery/join
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "activityId": 100001
}

### 手动开奖，演示环境可修改数据库 start_time 到当前时间之前
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lottery/draw
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "activityId": 100001
}

### 查询是否中奖
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lottery/100001/winner
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 我的订单
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
